        <div class="column has-text-left">
            <p>
                <h3 class="subtitle">OVERVIEW</h3>

                Our policy lasts 14 days, considering we provided the shipping for the specific sale. If 14 days have gone by since your purchase, unfortunately we canâ€™t offer you a refund or exchange.
